            <title>[LU-7725] Error unpacking OUT message</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7725</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I ran replay-dual test_26 with patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7716&quot; title=&quot;Do not do subdir check if source and target are in the same directory&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7716&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7716&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; applied, I can see the complaint as:&lt;/p&gt;

